cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human body pose estimation and attribute prediction using a parse graph. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel attribute and-or grammar model for joint inference of human attributes, part, and pose. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the training and evaluation of the proposed model. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with human body pose estimation and attribute prediction, which are important tasks in multimedia analysis. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also relevant as the paper discusses the modeling of the geometric articulation of the human body, which is important in robotics applications.
